31,"uid":336315,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:30:16.000Z","msg":"完全明白 日日過住咁既生活覺得好無意義<br />\n會有種生無可戀既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:26:06.000Z","msg":"所以我辭左職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ec726044e927f6d5faaf892988185c034e5b6f","tid":1678131,"uid":33058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"冇錢點生存"},{"pid":"801d73141782428a720c938af6877e7b30042655","tid":1678131,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779558ebbac3594eb094c960711c5cd3f1b62592","tid":1678131,"uid":295863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"I would  rather have a lowly paid job than a stressful and harsh one"},{"pid":"1f9d18279fc3abc1537de2e2ef0218eafa70cc18","tid":1678131,"uid":141782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:57:39.000Z","msg":"到冇工返又唔知生存為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有段時間冇野做 每朝起身都問自己起身黎有咩做"},{"pid":"1a3df6f256ce1c519813b1e38afe27fe164747c0","tid":1678131,"uid":169758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:40:53.000Z","msg":"希臘神話有一個故事<br />\n講述西西弗斯受到諸神嘅懲罰<br />\n要喺地獄不斷推一塊巨石上山<br />\n上到山頂，巨石又會自動碌返落山腳<br />\n佢每日都要重複呢種徒勞無功嘅工作，直到永恆<br />\n後人有一個講法<br />\n話諸神並唔係用「推石頭」嚟懲罰西西弗斯<br />\n而係用觀念<br />\n用「我永世都要推石頭實在太慘」嘅呢個觀念<br />\n西西弗斯知道自己改變唔到命運<br />\n佢唯一可以做嘅，就係繼續推石頭<br />\n直到有一日，佢發現佢可以蔑視自己嘅命運<br />\n甚至用享受呢個過程嚟去否定諸神對佢嘅懲罰<br />\n於是，佢感覺到自己係快樂嘅"},{"pid":"831ddec715be2fc5b25d53b72afd29fbca1a9a5a","tid":1678131,"uid":31765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:49:22.000Z","msg":"無供樓壓力 （有物業自住同收租）<br />\n銀行户口有幾球揸手<br />\n做緊份西工有幾萬蚊一個月想resign<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做又辛苦，唔做又唔捨得果幾雞野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e493f95f6ae5ee03f5aa6e3d689b39754b103f","tid":1678131,"uid":161749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:40:06.000Z","msg":"返工唔係爲錢唔通係愛同責任咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750897718219bc8b44523d203ab94c30fd989d83","tid":1678131,"uid":131339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b38e8ec394a9b67fbad94003d25d84d9378a4fbf","tid":1678131,"uid":300818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"番左工幾個月 每日都好無目標 日復一日<br />\n放工/放假都放鬆唔到 會諗起好快又要番公司做狗<br />\n老細躁底就唯有硬食 誰大誰惡誰正確<br />\n身邊同事都習慣哂呢啲生活<br />\n番工每日出8個鐘人工 但就好似買起你人生咁<br />\n真係覺得好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n究竟可以點樣調整心態 求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:42:24.000Z","msg":"用你賺到既錢做鐘意做既野"},{"pid":"038b16c4eccabbfa1a2686adc34e564339f12151","tid":1678131,"uid":228589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:47:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e619a1129a33dc8de4dc3ae71168c8ee0f39d63f","tid":1678131,"uid":110871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:11:53.000Z","msg":"而家返緊呢份好想resign<br />\n最主要人工低<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36af756efd3fbb32066bb765366fdae4dcbe597d","tid":1678131,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"返工為左出糧生存咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8add53076e72512f8b12cebad415631438b030e","tid":1678131,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"